	<div class="fusion-post-content-wrapper" style="padding:30px 25px 20px 25px;"><div class="fusion-post-content post-content"><h2 class="blog-shortcode-post-title entry-title"><a href="https://laboratories.telekom.com/13th-fokus-media-web-symposium-june-16th-18th-in-berlin/">13th FOKUS Media Web Symposium, June 16th-17th in Berlin</a></h2><p class="fusion-single-line-meta"><span class="vcard" style="display: none;"><span class="fn"><a href="https://laboratories.telekom.com/author/anja-kopperschmidt/" rel="author">Anja Kopperschmidt</a></span></span><span class="updated" style="display:none;">2026-06-29T13:25:41+02:00</span><span>June 12th, 2026</span><span class="fusion-inline-sep">|</span></p><div class="fusion-content-sep sep-none"></div><div class="fusion-post-content-container"><p>    "Serving Smarter: Predictive Resource Management in CDNsServing Smarter: Predictive Resource Management in CDNs" T-Labs , Peter Pogrzeba is speaking on the 13th FOKUS Media Web Symposium by Fraunhofer FOKUS on June 16-17 in Berlin In this presentation, he will showcase the results of our collaborative project with DT-Technik and ELTE University in Budapest. Peter Pogrzeba will demonstrate how advanced data analytics and AI-driven methods can be leveraged to significantly optimize energy consumption in a Content Delivery Network (CDN). Importantly, this optimization is achieved without compromising vital factors such as service quality (QoS, QoE) or operational reliability. [...]</p></div></div><div class="fusion-meta-info"><div class="fusion-alignleft"><a class="fusion-read-more" href="https://laboratories.telekom.com/13th-fokus-media-web-symposium-june-16th-18th-in-berlin/" aria-label="More on 13th FOKUS Media Web Symposium, June 16th-17th in Berlin">Read More</a></div></div></div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div></div>
</article>
