	<div class="fusion-post-content-wrapper" style="padding:30px 25px 20px 25px;"><div class="fusion-post-content post-content"><h2 class="blog-shortcode-post-title entry-title"><a href="https://laboratories.telekom.com/meet-us-at-deep-tech-momentum-in-berlin-may-20th-21st/">Join the masterclass at: Deep Tech Momentum in Berlin, May 20th-21st</a></h2><p class="fusion-single-line-meta"><span class="vcard" style="display: none;"><span class="fn"><a href="https://laboratories.telekom.com/author/anja-kopperschmidt/" rel="author">Anja Kopperschmidt</a></span></span><span class="updated" style="display:none;">2026-06-03T10:51:10+02:00</span><span>May 7th, 2026</span><span class="fusion-inline-sep">|</span></p><div class="fusion-content-sep sep-none"></div><div class="fusion-post-content-container"><p>    Masterclass From First Meeting to Real Impact: Inside a Startup–Corporate Collaboration That Worked (and What Didn’t) - register here What really happens when a deep tech startup meets a global corporation? In this interactive masterclass, Syntho (AI-driven synthetic data startup) and Deutsche Telekom take you behind the scenes of their year-long collaboration journey — from first contact at Deep Tech Momentum to a real-world proof of concept in telecom environments. Together, CEO Wim Kees Janssen and Deutsche Telekom’s Martin Martiska will share an unfiltered perspective on: How the collaboration started — and what almost stopped it [...]</p></div></div><div class="fusion-meta-info"><div class="fusion-alignleft"><a class="fusion-read-more" href="https://laboratories.telekom.com/meet-us-at-deep-tech-momentum-in-berlin-may-20th-21st/" aria-label="More on Join the masterclass at: Deep Tech Momentum in Berlin, May 20th-21st">Read More</a></div></div></div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div></div>
</article>
